{"tid":1390414,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"[repost]文宣組全面入場，連儂牆後另一大計","createTime":"2019-07-31T06:41:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T13:50:54.000Z","uid":272057,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"cbc96ff56cf0590a92a72cfd61818b5d9abaf230","tid":1390414,"uid":272057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:41:58.000Z","msg":"喂你地咁樣畫花啲銀紙係唔應該㗎 （光復香港 時代革命）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1385206/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1385206/page/1</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>呢條大計點解無人推,上面位ching真係天才</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我喺度正式宣佈大家唔好用銀紙做流動連儂牆，史稱「連儂錢」 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n平時D連儂牆成日俾班藍絲,撕子狗破壞，大家條氣都好唔gur<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但大家有冇諗過用銀紙做連儂牆，銀紙流動性高，香港人個個都唔會唔要，班藍絲,撕子狗收到都唔會破壞自己D錢咁on9，只能夠死死地氣袋住盡快搵方法用咗佢，<span style=\"color: maroon;\">呢個方法變相焗班藍絲,撕子狗做我地嘅宣傳機器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。</span> 而且，當佢地被自己友發現到自己有張反送中銀紙，佢地分分鐘互相猜疑、搞內訌，到時佢地鬼打鬼，我地就坐收漁人之利!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> p.s.但係係犯法架，雖然舉証好困難，但唔好做呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\">當全港所有銀紙都係宣傳工具，當政治完全融入生活，大家諗下到時民意會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n不建議方法:<br />\n每人用5張廿蚊紙，喺空白位一定要寫低<strong>六大訴求</strong>先，仲有空位就大家自由發揮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">最好就唔好超過一面嘅三分一</span></span>。搞掂就攞落去用左佢，收銀問起你就話收翻嚟已經係咁，你話係得呢一張佢都吹你唔漲，成件事好簡單但好有用。<br />\n<br />\n[六大訴求:撤回修例、釋放義士、收回暴動定性、成立獨立調查委員會，林鄭落台，立即實行雙真普選]<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pLe71x5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpLe71x5.jpg&h=2821bf98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\np.s.塗污鈔票其實是犯法行為。根據香港法例第200章《刑事罪行條例》第60條，「任何人無合法辯解而摧毀或損壞屬於他人的財產，意圖摧毀或損壞該財產或罔顧該財產是否會被摧毀或損壞，即屬犯罪」。大家千其唔好以身試法呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最重要 最重要 最重要唔好用中銀D銀紙寫呀，佢地要洗一大舊錢銷毀同重印架，好蝕架，唔好搞到D中資銀行啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"d7be65360822e8b24cfab1283939bad2823d50b1","tid":1390414,"uid":272057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:42:22.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"2696864937044411e17a5c3ae2abf91c1e3710b6","tid":1390414,"uid":272057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:13:25.000Z","msg":"求推"},{"pid":"7bbb35bc25044c7db8292e59070c2e57f0d339f5","tid":1390414,"uid":272057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:14:12.000Z","msg":"求推"},{"pid":"f9c0ce426f138497d02648178a25c75a42f719c5","tid":1390414,"uid":272057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:14:26.000Z","msg":"求推"},{"pid":"75edb879a4b8eb07d5efa537d1719891f1254652","tid":1390414,"uid":272057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:15:05.000Z","msg":"求推"},{"pid":"25c98c31710fb150271a5b3868f34391e8dd44b5","tid":1390414,"uid":272057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:15:17.000Z","msg":"求推"},{"pid":"a4a84344ab1ae07dc6947f1623067105af98c017","tid":1390414,"uid":272057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:15:29.000Z","msg":"求推"},{"pid":"afc70c5d45d010f47ddc5054614353231f818670","tid":1390414,"uid":2720